{
  "script_id": "tessellation",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "tessellation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tessellation/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "看看浴室墙上的瓷砖，一块挨着一块，铺得严丝合缝。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tessellation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tessellation/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.72,
      "size": 27504,
      "text": "为什么它们之间不留一点缝隙，也不会互相重叠？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tessellation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tessellation/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "这种把平面铺满的方式，数学上叫做密铺，或者镶嵌。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tessellation",
      "section_id": "angle",
      "line_id": "ang-1",
      "filename": "angle-ang-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tessellation/xiaoxiao/angle-ang-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.64,
      "size": 26208,
      "text": "密铺的关键，藏在多边形聚拢的那个顶点上。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tessellation",
      "section_id": "angle",
      "line_id": "ang-2",
      "filename": "angle-ang-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tessellation/xiaoxiao/angle-ang-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.24,
      "size": 35856,
      "text": "若干个角挤在一个点周围，它们的和必须正好是360度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tessellation",
      "section_id": "angle",
      "line_id": "ang-3",
      "filename": "angle-ang-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tessellation/xiaoxiao/angle-ang-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.24,
      "size": 35856,
      "text": "多一点就重叠，少一点就留缝，只有刚好360度才能铺平。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tessellation",
      "section_id": "three",
      "line_id": "thr-1",
      "filename": "three-thr-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tessellation/xiaoxiao/three-thr-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "正三角形内角60度，六个拼成360度，铺得满满当当。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tessellation",
      "section_id": "three",
      "line_id": "thr-2",
      "filename": "three-thr-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tessellation/xiaoxiao/three-thr-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "正方形内角90度，四个一拼刚好360度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tessellation",
      "section_id": "three",
      "line_id": "thr-3",
      "filename": "three-thr-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tessellation/xiaoxiao/three-thr-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "正六边形内角120度，三个就够360度，这就是蜂巢的形状。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tessellation",
      "section_id": "three",
      "line_id": "thr-4",
      "filename": "three-thr-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tessellation/xiaoxiao/three-thr-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.53,
      "size": 40464,
      "text": "正五边形内角108度，无论几个都凑不出360度，所以铺不满。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tessellation",
      "section_id": "semi",
      "line_id": "semi-1",
      "filename": "semi-semi-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tessellation/xiaoxiao/semi-semi-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "如果允许几种正多边形混搭，还能拼出更多花样。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tessellation",
      "section_id": "semi",
      "line_id": "semi-2",
      "filename": "semi-semi-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tessellation/xiaoxiao/semi-semi-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "这类混合的规则密铺，被称为半正则镶嵌。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tessellation",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tessellation/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "切换三角形、正方形、正六边形，看它们如何铺满整个画面。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tessellation",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tessellation/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "留意每个顶点，你会发现角度总是刚好合成一整圈。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tessellation",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tessellation/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.5,
      "size": 24048,
      "text": "密铺就是用多边形不留缝地铺满平面。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tessellation",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tessellation/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.09,
      "size": 49392,
      "text": "条件是顶点处角度和为360度，单一正多边形只有三、四、六边形做得到。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tessellation",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tessellation/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "简单的角度规则，铺出无尽的秩序之美，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 35.449999999999996,
